---
description: Type-aware reverse lookup of a Go symbol. Use before renaming a function or changing a signature.
allowed-tools: Bash(gofasta xrefs*)
argument-hint: <symbol>  (e.g. UserService or app/services.UserService.Create)
---

Run `gofasta xrefs $ARGUMENTS --json`. Report the definition location
and every reference site (file, line, enclosing function). If the
result is `AMBIGUOUS_SYMBOL`, ask the user which package they meant
and re-run with the fully-qualified form.
